# Website Meeting Meta Chips

Applies when rendering a meeting's type, lifecycle status, or invite-notify status on the customer portal (directory cards, home focus status card, details header).

Flow: `docs/platforms/website/flow-customer-meetings.md` ¬ß4.1‚Äì¬ß4.2; home consumer: `flow-customer-shell.md` ¬ß7.

## Rule

Render each meeting axis (type, status, notify) as its own `MeetingMetaChips` pill ‚Äî leading Feather icon + resolved label + scheme-aware tone. Do NOT concatenate the three into one `¬∑`-joined `Text` line: joining conflates lifecycle status with notify status and reads as ambiguous.

Consumers that must use chips (not `metaLine`):

- `CustomerMeetingCard` (directory, home ‚Äúothers‚Äù, details basics reuse)
- `CustomerHomeStatusCard` (command-hero focus summary)
- `CustomerMeetingDetailsScreen` header under `SectionHeading`

- One distinct icon per enum value (no icon reused across axes); one tone per value.
- Tone colors come from `semanticColor`: soft feedback fill (`stateSoft*`) as chip background paired with the matching `state*` foreground (icon + text); `neutral` uses `sectionBrandBackground` / `iconSecondary` / `textSecondary`. Both resolve per light/dark automatically ‚Äî no per-scheme branching, no hardcoded hex.
- Unified `caption` weight across chips (no per-chip bold).
- Empty axis label ‚Üí omit that chip; all empty ‚Üí render `null`.

## Discriminator props (W42 still holds)

Pass the enum **value** (`typeValue` / `statusValue` / `notifyStatusValue`) alongside the already-resolved label. The value is an icon/tone discriminator only ‚Äî the presentational component still receives resolved label strings and does NOT translate (see `.cursor/rules/website-presentational-label-props.mdc`).

## Data

`notify_status { value label }` must be selected on the meeting **list** query (`useCustomerMeetings.ts`), not only on details, so directory cards can render the notify chip. Home focus status comes from `useCustomerHome` focus meeting / status slices (already includes `notify_status` when the focus payload carries it).

## Forbidden

- `[typeLabel, statusLabel, notifyStatusLabel].join(" ¬∑ ")` (or any joined meta string) for these axes ‚Äî including `CustomerHomeStatusCard`.
- Hardcoded state colors instead of `semanticColor.stateSoft*` / `semanticColor.state*`.
- Reusing the same icon for two different values.

